name: Experiment Or Die #100
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. 10th letter in The Cool Alphabet, O Is For Optimus. Growing up in the 80's there wasn't much that was cooler than Transformers and Optimus was the leader of the good guys! The toy that became an animated show that became a toy that became a really successful movie franchise. These characters and stories are imprinted on our lives now and will be a part of us forever. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
